title: CROQUETTES CHAT WITH SORGHO ADULT - Tomojo
descriptions: Our pet food for cats is rich in protein and suitable for sensitive animals thanks to its limited number of allergens. Made with sorghum, a cereal with antioxidant properties, our recipe is formulated with veterinarians to provide all the essential nutrients for your pet. And of course our pet food contains no antibiotics or artificial preservatives.
Each pack of pet food for cats is packaged in biodegradable packaging and saves 130 litres of water compared to pet food with beef.
ingredients: a mixture of plants rich in natural saponins (Yucca schidigera juice, Camellia sp. Quillaja saponaria, Chenopodium quinoa)
additive: 3a370 Taurine: 1365 mg/kg. Trace elements : E1 Iron : 91 mg
Amino acids: DL Methionine (3c301) : 1820 mg. Technological additives: Preservatives
